---
title: Loaded Pork & Black Bean Chilli with Basmati Rice & Cheddar Cheese
description: Pop go the black beans in this fully loaded chilli! Fry them in a dry pan to make them crispy on the outside with a fluffy centre, the perfect topper for a soul-satisfying chilli made with pork mince, warming spices and veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d81bf3394345f429b7d5abb-9b5ebae9.jpg
